ButtonFactory
public class ButtonFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements IButtonFactory, javax.swing.SwingConstants

Default button factory implementation for JYSearchField. Optional UI-properties:

  • JYSearchField.searchButton.icon [.disabled | .pressed | .hover] - String, Icon path or className
  • JYSearchField.searchButton.insets - Insets, specifies empty border size, default is 0 1 0 4
  • JYSearchField.searchButton.toolTip - String, tool tip
  • JYSearchField.searchPopupButton.icon [.disabled | .pressed | .hover] - String, Icon path or className
  • JYSearchField.searchPopupButton.insets - Insets, specifies empty border size, default is 0 1 0 4
  • JYSearchField.deleteButton.icon [.disabled | .pressed | .hover][.selected] - String, Icon path or className
  • JYSearchField.deleteButton.insets - Insets, specifies empty border size, default is 0 2 0 0
  • JYSearchField.deleteButton.toolTip - String, tool tip

    • Version:
    1.10, 21.01.2011
